snippet.title: Pro Yakyuu Spirits 5 (PS3) - Gameplay
snippet.description:
A full game of the PlayStation 3 version of Pro Yakyuu Spirits 5, a 2008 baseball video game by Konami. Yomiuri Giants at Yakult Swallows, starring Koji Uehara and Norichika Aoki. 

You can check out video from the PlayStation 2 version here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sDMLOJOvhxM
